{
  "stem": "11274.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then I said, oh, what am I going to say when I come home, and tell mom I just watched Father-- my father getting killed?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I jumped in front of them, I said, you want to kill my father-- I said, I was naive-- and I said, I'm a young girl, and-- and-- maybe it's going to make some difference that I'm gonna beg.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I said, if you're going to shoot my father, you're going to have to shoot him through me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they started laughing, and making fun of me, calling him Jewish names-- the-- look at the Jewess, and some other derogatory names.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She thinks that we're gonna be caring about her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they got the guns.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And before that incident happened, I was doing sewing, as I said, and one time a German officer came over to the window, knocked into-- they weren't allowed to come into the house, as far as we know, because they never went to any Jewish home-- and knocked on the window.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I opened the window, he said, I've got some sheets, here, could you make me two pillowcases?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very-- could you-- didn't order anything-- would you?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, oh, yes, sure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes, sir, yes, sir.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I took the sheets, and I made the pillowcases.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When, I said-- if you could-- when are they going to be ready, I had some of the work to do that I needed for-- for a living, to make.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I said, is in a week OK?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Oh, yes, that's OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He came a week later, he picked up the pillowcases, and then he came another time for his friend to make two pillowcases.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Both times he left me some money.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
